**Everything you need is in `.agent/` folders - workspace-level for shared (if multi-project), project-level for specific.**

## üìù Adaptation Notes

This is a generic template. Adapt the following to your project:

- **Project paths**: Replace `[project]`, `[frontend-project]`, `[backend-project]` with your actual project names
- **Workspace structure**: If you have a single project (not a monorepo), you may only have one `.agent/` folder
- **Session checklist**: The session start checklist is optional - only if you have `.agent/SYSTEM/ai/SESSION-START-CHECKLIST.md`
- **Critical rules**: The critical rules file is optional - only if you have `.agent/SYSTEM/critical/CRITICAL-NEVER-DO.md`
